{"title":"Set the alarm for 5:00","description":"Turn on the alarm clock on 5:00 with sound. 5 hours   alarm clock. Free and simple alarm online. Set alarm for 5 hours  .","content":"Is there a need to set an alarm for 5 hours  ? Use our simple and free alarm clock online! \nSet the alarm for 5 hours   or choose another time by setting it yourself or by selecting from the list. An alarm clock with a sound that you can set yourself. After setting the time, press the **Add** button to turn on the alarm.\n\nTurn on the alarm clock for 5 hours   and go about your business, the alarm clock will definitely notify you at exactly 5:00.\n\nAll alarms are saved in your browser, so you can reuse them. The clock beautifully shows the time remaining from 5 hours  , with an accuracy of seconds and milliseconds."}